---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="ICMR Guidelines - Indian Nutrition Standards | Mizan"
  description="Understand ICMR-NIN 2024 dietary guidelines for Indians. Daily limits for sodium, sugar, fat, and recommended intake values."
>
  <article class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">

      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-mizan-teal">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">‚Ä∫</span>
        <a href="/samjho" class="hover:text-mizan-teal">Samjho</a>
        <span class="mx-2">‚Ä∫</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700">ICMR Guidelines</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-5xl">üáÆüá≥</span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-2">
          ICMR-NIN 2024 Guidelines
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-mizan-teal">Indian Nutrition Standards</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">4 min read</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          ICMR (Indian Council of Medical Research) aur NIN (National Institute of Nutrition) ne
          2024 mein updated dietary guidelines release ki hain ‚Äî specifically Indians ke liye designed.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-amber-warning/10 border border-amber-warning/30 rounded-xl p-5 my-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Kyun Indian-specific?</strong> Humare genetics, diet patterns, aur health conditions
            Western countries se alag hain. WHO guidelines directly apply nahi hoti.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Daily Limits (Per Day)</h2>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse my-6">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-gray-200">
                <th class="py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Nutrient</th>
                <th class="py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Daily Limit</th>
                <th class="py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Notes</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-gray-700">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium">Energy</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4">2000 kcal</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500">Sedentary adult reference</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium">Sodium</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-red-critical font-bold">2000 mg</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500">~5g salt (1 tsp)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium">Free Sugars</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-red-critical font-bold">50g</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500">&lt;10% of total calories</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium">Saturated Fat</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-red-critical font-bold">22g</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500">&lt;10% of total calories</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium">Total Fat</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4">65g</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500">~30% of calories</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium">Protein</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-green-safe font-bold">55g</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500">RDA for reference adult</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium">Fiber</td>
                <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-green-safe font-bold">30g</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500">Minimum recommended</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Key Recommendations</h2>

        <div class="space-y-4 my-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="text-xl">1Ô∏è‚É£</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Reduce Salt Intake</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Most Indians consume 9-10g salt daily ‚Äî double the limit!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="text-xl">2Ô∏è‚É£</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Limit Added Sugars</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sugary drinks and packaged snacks main culprits hain.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="text-xl">3Ô∏è‚É£</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Increase Protein</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">73% Indians are protein deficient. Focus on daal, eggs, dairy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="text-xl">4Ô∏è‚É£</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Eat More Fiber</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Whole grains, vegetables, fruits ‚Äî processed foods mein fiber kam hota hai.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">How Mizan Uses These</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Jab hum <strong>"Roz ki Hadd"</strong> calculate karte hain, hum ICMR limits use karte hain.
          For example, agar ek product mein 1000mg sodium per 100g hai, toh safe limit 40g hoga
          (20% of daily 2000mg).
        </p>

        <div class="bg-mizan-teal/10 border border-mizan-teal/30 rounded-xl p-6 mt-10">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-mizan-teal mb-3">Official Source</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Full guidelines ICMR-NIN website pe available hain. 178 pages ka detailed document hai.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.nin.res.in/nutrition2020/RDA_short_report.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-mizan-teal hover:underline font-medium">
            Download ICMR-NIN RDA Report (PDF) ‚Üí
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 flex justify-between">
        <a href="/samjho/mizan-score" class="text-mizan-teal hover:underline">‚Üê Mizan Score</a>
        <a href="/samjho/hidden-sugar" class="text-mizan-teal hover:underline">Next: Hidden Sugars ‚Üí</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
